{
  "stem": "25598.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were kept beside the synagogue wall there-- heaps and mountains of people that were frozen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they froze to one another.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it became one big mountain of frozen dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And people would go and look at their children, or their grandparents, or their aunts, or their uncle.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, when spring came, it was a mad rush to bury these people before they decay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because that is another way of spreading epidemics, and because it would have been also much too painful-- more painful for people to see them decay.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only way to bury these people was to hack them to pieces from the frozen mountain-- to hack lumps of that frozen mountain of dead and bury them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father just became broken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father had pitch black hair and blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in a few days, his hair changed to white.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I've never seen anything like this in my life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My mother couldn't handle the-- the dirt and the whole environment that we lived in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And her way out of this was she became paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it was almost like psychologically, she couldn't do anything about it, so she had immobilized her body too.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't do anything about it anyways, so here I am.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm a blob of nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And for a year, she-- she didn't move.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The lower-- the lower part of her body was paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In order for us to all sleep in that hut, the men had built from wooden planks low-- like low structures.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the reason for this was so that some people can sleep underneath, and some people can sleep on top, because there wasn't enough room for everybody to sleep on-- on the floor-- on the dirt floor.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
